"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot01\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/7eb0a55ae5d61396_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/h5.sinaimg.cn\/upload\/100\/721\/2019\/03\/14\/vote.png\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/7eb0a55ae5d61396_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#朱丹叫错陈立农名字#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">#朱丹叫错陈立农名字# 10日，朱丹在主持过程中再次发生口误，将陈立农错叫成“赵立农”，随后，朱丹发文向陈立农道歉，“对于今天所发生的失误，我非常抱歉，也谢谢你在舞台上的包容。”陈立农则回复道：“没事的朱丹姐！”表示自己是新人，会继续努力的。#阿乐今日问# ：你会因为被叫错名字而生气吗？ ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/a3a4c3f5a6fbb686_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot02\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/a3a4c3f5a6fbb686_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/imgaliyuncdn.miaopai.com\/images\/AjHoFQcpWK-vuY~V1rCnvzsEtmZRQxkrqG0zpA___mq1r_4.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/a3a4c3f5a6fbb686_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#袁隆平路边小店理发16年#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">【#袁隆平路边小店理发16年#：怕围观趁没人才去，剪完会说“我又年轻了”[太开心]】从2003年开始，袁隆平就在一家不起眼的小理发店里理发。因为担心自己出现会引起围观，影响理发店生意，他每次都趁店里没人的时候才去。理发师曹女士称，袁老自己设计发型，剪完会俏皮地说“哈，我又年轻了”。 ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/a0e96bd880956cb4_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot03\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/a0e96bd880956cb4_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/61e7f4aaly1g9rsgtqm41j20n40qeu0x.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/a0e96bd880956cb4_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#雪莉尸检结果#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">#雪莉最终尸检结果# #雪莉尸检结果# 据韩媒，警方相关人士10日表示，上周国立科学调查研究院接到了“雪莉并非因外部力量或药物死亡”的最终尸检结果，目前该事件处于检方指挥阶段。该相关人士就雪莉的死亡时间表示“推测是在收到报案前一天晚上午夜前后几个小时内死亡。”据悉，10月16日，国立科学调查 ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/643271e24353e0c6_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot04\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/643271e24353e0c6_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/wx4.sinaimg.cn\/orj480\/628aabfdly1g9rx1fito4j20zk0k0wux.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/643271e24353e0c6_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#周冬雨获澳门影后#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">#澳门国际影展#周冬雨凭借《少年的你》获得新华语映像·最佳女主角，冬雨的感言——\n\n“谢谢澳门影展，然后谢谢《少年的你》剧组，我爱你们。希望大家借由这部电影，更多的关注校园暴力，希望有更多的人得到帮助。\n\n哎，《少年的你》剧组，（台上做出比心表情。）”http:\/\/t.cn\/AieBOefD  ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/78e73ec19923f00d_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot05\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/78e73ec19923f00d_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/c9acb938ly1g9ruz61p0xj20qo0ys445.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/78e73ec19923f00d_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#李子柒做过电音DJ#<\/a><\/